es-3\";i:2;s:10:\"archives-3\";}}',0,'https://central.wordcamp.test/?post_type=jetpack_migration&p=69191',0,'jetpack_migration','',0),(69192,1,'2019-07-05 23:27:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2019-07-05 23:27:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://central.wordcamp.test/?p=69192',0,'post','',0),(69193,1,'2019-07-05 23:48:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2019-07-05 23:48:39','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://central.wordcamp.test/?p=69193',0,'post','',0),(1834651,1,'2014-02-19 21:02:59','2014-02-19 21:02:59','<a href=\"https://central.wordcamp.org/files/2014/02/WCSF13-crowd.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-1834654 alignright\" src=\"https://central.wordcamp.org/files/2014/02/WCSF13-crowd-300x168.jpg\" alt=\"WordCamp San Francisco Overview\" width=\"300\" height=\"168\" /></a>Do you love sponsoring WordCamps? Perhaps you love it so much that you wish you could sponsor every WordCamp on the planet. If so, check out our <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/community/2019-wordpress-global-community-sponsorship-program/\">2019 Global Community Sponsorship Package</a>, a great way for companies to sponsor multiple WordPress community events with ease.\n\nThe Global Community Sponsorship program allows most WordCamps to spend substantially less time worrying about fundraising, freeing up our volunteer organizing teams to focus on putting great speakers and content in front of WordCamp attendees. If you\'re hoping to contribute to improving and sustaining WordPress community events, this is a great way to do so.\n\n<a href=\"https://central.wordcamp.org/files/2013/09/pic1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-1137494\" src=\"https://central.wordcamp.org/files/2013/09/pic1-300x253.jpg\" alt=\"pic1\" width=\"199\" height=\"169\" /></a>As a Global Community Sponsor, you\'ll be notified by email every time a WordCamp in your selected region/time period is added to the schedule. That email will include the WordCamp\'s date, location, shipping address, sponsor wrangler contact info, twitter account, hashtag, expected attendance figures, and more. You\'ll be billed quarterly by WordCamp Central, so you won\'t have to maintain multiple lines of communication (unless you just want to). WordCamps will be notified of your sponsorship at the point of budget approval -- the same time they\'re going on the official schedule -- so you\'ll be among the first sponsors acknowledged by each local WordCamp organizing team.\n\nInterested in becoming a Global Community Sponsor? <a href=\"mailto:support@wordcamp.org?Subject=Multi-event%20Sponsorship%20inquiry\" target=\"_top\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Drop us a line!</a>\n\nHuge props to the community group that helped draft the first iteration of this program back in 2012: <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/profile/adavis3105\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Al Davis</a>, <a href=\"http://profiles.wordpress.org/kcristiano\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Kevin Cristiano</a>, <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/profile/jared_smith\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jared Smith</a>, and <a href=\"http://wordpress.org/support/profile/missmariss\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Marissa Rosen</a>. And to the sponsors of every WordCamp, thank you for helping us make great WordPress events possible.','Sponsor Multiple WordCamps','','publish','open','open','','sponsor-multiple-wordcamps','','','2014-02-19 21:02:59','2014-02-19 21:02:59','',0,'https://central.wordcamp.org/?page_id=1834651',0,'page','',0),(2321820,1,'2014-05-16 16:17:08','2014-05-16 16:17:08','[polldaddy type=\"iframe\" survey=\"2848A97C8D757605\" height=\"auto\" domain=\"wordcampcentral\" id=\"wordcamp-incident-report\"]','WordCamp Incident Report','','publish','open','open','','wordcamp-incident-report','','','2014-05-16 16:17:08','2014-05-16 16:17:08','',0,'https://ce